About us
Award-winning RC Otter's Island Eats is a place for the whole family! Located in the Heart of Old Captiva Village with lovely shopping and dining, you enjoy live music daily with dining inside and outside.
Nearly 100 menu items are available. Kids Menu too. Come on out to Captiva & eat at Otters!! Pet friendly & if they don't bite we allow people also.
We play live music every day from 12:00 to 10:00 pm There's outdoor/indoor seating available & we are dog friendly. Seafood, Pasta, Salads, Ribs, Burgers, Soups, and Sandwiches. There's even a kid's menu.
